---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Notice | K & D Auto Electric" description="Privacy notice for K & D Auto Electric, Inc. in Somerset, PA." canonical="https://kdautoelectric.com/privacy-notice">
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-kd-black via-kd-gray-900 to-kd-red/20 py-16">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="text-sm text-kd-gray-400 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-kd-yellow transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-kd-yellow">Privacy Notice</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-kd-white">Privacy Notice</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-kd-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-gray">
      <p class="text-sm text-kd-gray-500">Last updated: October 13, 2022</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you contact us through our website, phone, or email, we may collect information you provide directly, such as your name, phone number, email address, and vehicle information. We also collect standard web analytics data including page views and site usage patterns.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your information solely for the purpose of providing our automotive services, responding to your inquiries, and improving our website and services. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Our website uses Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our site. Google may use cookies and similar technologies to collect standard analytics data. You can learn more about Google&apos;s privacy practices at their Privacy &amp; Terms site.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy notice, please contact us at:</p>
      <p>
        K &amp; D Auto Electric, Inc.<br />
        212 Forward Boulevard<br />
        Somerset, PA 15501<br />
        (814) 443-3615
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
